## Option 1: Hugging Face Inference API (EASIEST - 100% FREE)

**âœ¨ Best for quick setup**

### Steps:
1. Go to https://huggingface.co (create free account)
2. Click Profile â†’ Settings â†’ Access Tokens
3. Create new token (Read access is enough)
4. In Comet chat, enter your HF token
5. Done! Uses Llama 2, Mistral models FREE

**Pros:**
- Completely free, no credit card
- Instant setup
- Multiple open-source models
- Community-driven

**Models Available:**
- meta-llama/Llama-2-7b-chat
- mistralai/Mistral-7B-Instruct
- google/flan-t5-large

