## How to Use in Comet Chat Browser

### Integration:

```javascript
// cloud-llm-integration.js handles everything!
// Just include it in chat.html:

<script src="cloud-llm-integration.js"></script>

// Automatic provider detection:
const llm = new CloudLLMIntegration();
await llm.sendMessage("Your message here");
```

### Setting Up Credentials:

1. Open Comet chat interface
2. Click settings
3. Choose your provider (HF/Azure/Replicate)
4. Paste your API key
5. Save
6. Start chatting!

